Ten civilians and one police officer were killed in a gun and bomb attack by Al-Shabaab fighters on an upscale beachfront hotel in Somalia's capital on Sunday, an official told AFP.Security forces took four hours to regain control of the Elite Hotel in Mogadishu after five assailants stormed it early Sunday evening.AFP 
